    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "August 10, 1961",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Mr. William C. Sullivan",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Chief Inspector",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "AIR FORCE",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Sullivan:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Our company possesses a guest house on a mountain top",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Southwest of Carlisle.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "A number of us were holding a meeting Tuesday Evening,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "August 8. It was warm and we were sitting on an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "uncovered veranda.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "At two minutes of ten we noted a bright light over-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "head longitudinally but a few degrees Northwest",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "latitudinally. It moved in an East by North direction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "At five minutes after ten it disappeared behind the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "tree tops.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "The night was clear, stars were plainly visible. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "North star provided a sense of direction. The light",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "was brighter than any star.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "As we followed the course of the light it seemed to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "move a bit erratically from side to side and on a few",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "occasions seemed to jump ahead. Though all of us",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "observed these variable movements, I recognize they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "could be attributed to atmospheric conditions or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "eye concentration.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "I have been at a loss as to whether to report",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "and, if so, to whom.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "REC-32 62-8555-292",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "I would like to assure you that the light observed was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "not an airplane. With the sky so full of \"exotic",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "objects\" one hesitates to report any observation today.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
